Cofinimmo Buys Nursing Home, Sees Gross Initial Yield of 6.5%

-- B y   J o h n   M a r t e n s
-- 
2011-10-13T16:17:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/cofinimmo-buys-nursing-home-sees-gross-initial-yield-of-6-5-.html
Cofinimmo (COFB)  SA agreed to buy a nursing
home in Brussels for 6.5 million euros and plans to spend an
additional 10 million euros on renovation and expansion works
for a gross initial rental yield of 6.5 percent starting in the
fourth quarter of 2012.  Cofinimmo also said it agreed to construct a new nursing
home in the Brussels periphery in a joint development with  Le
Noble Age. (LNA)   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Martens at 
 jmartens1@bloomberg.net  